These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
House: cape-cod, palace, craftsman
1. the palace house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
3. the cape-cod house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| House   | craftsman | palace | cape-cod |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, february
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Birthday   | april | february | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, punk, disco
1. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
2. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Music-Genre   | folk | punk | disco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, golf
1. the person who's sport is swimming is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Sport   | rowing | golf | swimming |

 #################################

 
