.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, bridge
1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing backgammon is the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |    3    |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon | bridge |

