.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, blue, emerald
1. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes blue is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Color   | blue | emerald | lavender |

 